Item.Description: Generate Bloomberg requests for FX Spot IPV

col.string: DatabaseItems("\\\MD_SILVER", "Murex IPV FX Spots", "Murex FX Spot", "*").WHERE((|Is Currency Relevant| = TRUE) AND ((|Is Currency Quoted By ECB| = TRUE) OR (|Is Precious Metal| = TRUE)) AND (NOT ISERROR(|Ask Price|('Murex').Data(%RunDate%))))
